<node><name>Do a Connotation Interview</name>
<id>20</id>
<lefticon>group</lefticon>
<righticon>discuss</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Work in pairs to interview and analyse one another. Ask your partner to answer the question:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;If you were a [category], what would you be?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Possible categories (car, beverage, animal, superhero, Montreal neighborhood, time of day, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note:  Refrain from explaining responses, leaving the partner to interpret connotations.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
<textheight>174</textheight>
